1
00:00:02,720 --> 00:00:06,000
(Jin) Web Micro-Drama Review No. (2025) 003

2
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:12,320
Zhang Yuehua

3
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:24,360
Fei Yufei

4
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:26,280
I see that you've been very busy lately,

5
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:28,800
so I had the kitchen make some snacks

6
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:32,159
and brought them over especially for you.

7
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:37,480
Li Tianfen

8
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:40,010
My father is still waiting for you in the room.

9
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:42,120
You've been tied up with official business these days.

10
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,920
That's enough for you to worry about.

11
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:46,080
Ding Lei

12
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:48,680
Why don't I go talk to the Yao family for you?

13
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:48,320
Ding Lei

14
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,850
I have my own plans for the wedding.

15
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:54,080
I'm just worried about you.

16
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:59,080
Ding Doudou

17
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:03,340
It is my duty to work hard for the Song family.

18
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,040
Just enjoy yourself.

19
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,040
Xiao,

20
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,320
just take good care of my father and brother.

21
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:07,320
Xiao Wei.

22
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:15,560
Ding Binbin, Wu Liting.

23
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,200
Jin Xueyu, Liu Mengjunyu, Liu Hong.

24
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,850
The bracelet seems to have rolled down there.

25
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:41,000
Li Huan.

26
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,760
Don't try to provoke me like this.

27
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:29,400
Zhang Yuehua.

28
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:01,040
How did you fall down the stairs?

29
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:05,140
How were the servants looking after you?

30
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,040
I was careless.

31
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:11,600
But Huainan is getting married soon.

32
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,920
How can I attend like this?

33
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:17,280
Why don't we postpone his wedding?

34
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:21,410
We've already settled it with the Yao family.

35
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,040
Since your face is injured and you can't go,

36
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:24,640
you should just rest at home.

37
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,400
Alright, alright.

38
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,920
Here, have a seat first.

39
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,840
It's your wedding with Huainan,

40
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:01,080
so it's inconvenient for you to see guests.

41
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:03,610
While they are socializing in the front hall,

42
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:10,520
take this as a wedding gift for you both.

43
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,760
I went to a lot of trouble to get it.

44
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,520
You really must try some.

45
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,240
You are so thoughtful, Stepmother.

46
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,800
From now on, we are all family.

47
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,960
If you need anything, just ask me.

48
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:26,080
Don't treat me like a stranger.

49
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:38,240
Then let me thank you first, Stepmother.

50
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,060
I'm still a bit thin-skinned.

51
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:33,260
Spit it out! There's something wrong with the wine.

52
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:55,890
Marrying into the Song family is no laughing matter.

53
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,160
Take her away.

54
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:04,800
She spat most of it out.

55
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,880
Yao Shengsheng, get up.

